==English==

===Etymology===
From late Latin ''[[hebdomad#Latin|hebdomad]]'', from Greek [[ἑβδομάς]] ‘group of seven’, from [[ἑπτά]] ‘seven’.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈhɛbdəmæd/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A group of [[seven]]
# A period of a seven days, a [[week]].
# (''Gnosticism'') A group of seven superhuman beings.

